name: a.goblin.life
description:
Uses tensorflow and your browser to process webcam + microphone inputs to rotoscope VRMs and transform your voice into another's. 

 WASD > Move 

QE > Rotate

 Enter > Chat

     ~ > Command

 Space > Jump

 Default Binds:

 N: Selfie

 M: NotSelfie

 H: Hi | Hi! | Hello | Heya | Yo

 F1: Help

 F2: NotHelp
